<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>


    <div style="width:100%; max-width: 750px; margin:auto; margin-top: 0px !important; padding-top:0px !important; font-family: 'Helvetica', san-serif;">
      <img src="https://thinmanager.com/images/email_headers/EventCancelationNoticeHeader.jpg" width="100%" alt="Thank you for registering" style="border-bottom:1px solid #272727;" />

      <div style="margin-top: 45px; padding-left:25px; padding-right: 25px;">
        
        <p>Dear <%= @user.firstname %>,</p>
        
        <p>This message is simply to confirm that you have canceled your registration for an upcoming event with our team. Please check the details below.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:35px;">Event Details</h3>

        <p style="line-height:18pt;">
          <b>Name:</b> <%= @event.name %><br />
          <b>Description:</b> <%= @event.description %><br />
          <b>Date:</b> <%= @event.starttime.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>As long as there is still open reservation space in the event, please feel free to re-register if your schedule allows. Also, if you did not mean for this cancelation to occur, please <%= link_to "contact us", "mailto:events@thinmanager.com" %>.</p>

        <p>To view more events upcoming with ThinManager, please check <a href="https://partners.thinmanager.com/events" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
        <br />
        <p>Thank you,</p>

        <p>The ThinManager Team</p>

      </div>
      

    </div>

      


  </body>
  </html>